value: /* This program creates the stacked data and runs the stacked DD analysis presented in Appendix Table 7, panel A */
*CHANGE THE FOLLOWING DIRECTORIES TO BE YOUR DIRECTORIES

/*

*NOTE - this commented out code creates the final stacked analysis file that I attach and run the analysis with

*BRING IN CLEANED CCD DATA
use stacked_dd.dta

*********************************************************************************

* Arizona Missing revenune data for 1987-1989
drop if fipst==4 & year1==1987
drop if fipst==4 & year1==1988

* Drop Alaska
drop if fipst==2

* Year Ordered Prefered coding 
gen sfr_year1=0
replace sfr_year1=1991 if stfips==21     /* Kentucky 1989 Court Effective 1990-91, LE*/
/* Tenessee 1992, Education Improvement Act, Fully funded 1997-98 */
/* Colorado 1994 Main Leg., LRS use 2000 Leg, implemented 2001*/
/* Wyoming LRS use 2001 Leg but 1995 was Major Court Case */
/* Ohio Court 1997 & 2002 with funding increase in 2001 */
/* Note: Need to change this if don't use early events */
/* New York Court 2003 1st 2006 Main, leg. State Education Budget and Reform Act of 2007.  */

varlist.value:
", replace
	cells(b(star fmt(%9.3f)) se(par)) starlevels(* 0.10 ** 0.05 *** 0.01) stats(N, fmt(0) labels("
